BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Pride & Prejudice
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20270115T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20270115T213000
DTSTAMP:20260712T153920Z
UID:occ-1278@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Play
DESCRIPTION:Austen's comedy of courtship in a fast\, playful adaptation 
 — Lizzy Bennet swears off marriage\; Darcy keeps turning up.\n\nJane Aus
 ten's 1813 comedy of courtship\, here in a loose\, high-energy adaptation 
 that treats the marriage plot as a game with real stakes. Lizzy Bennet has
  decided she will never marry. Then Mr. Darcy — aggravating\, and only v
 aguely handsome by her account — keeps crossing her path. Presented by A
 rcadia Theater\, the Alpharetta community theatre.
GEO:34.0765277;-84.2884766
LAST-MODIFIED:20260712T153742Z
LOCATION:Arcadia Theater\, 180 Academy St
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://www.simpletix.com/e/pride-prejudice-tickets-279864
END:VEVENT
