BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Stage Kiss
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20270219T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20270219T213000
DTSTAMP:20260712T153920Z
UID:occ-1287@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Play
DESCRIPTION:Sarah Ruhl's comedy: two exes cast as lovers in a creaky 1930s
  melodrama\, and the kissing gets complicated.\n\nSarah Ruhl's backstage c
 omedy about two actors with a shared romantic past who land opposite each 
 other as the leads in a forgotten 1930s melodrama. The script requires the
 m to kiss\, repeatedly\, and the line between playing lovers and being the
 m starts to dissolve. A community production from Arcadia Theater.
GEO:34.0765277;-84.2884766
LAST-MODIFIED:20260712T153742Z
LOCATION:Arcadia Theater\, 180 Academy St
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://www.simpletix.com/e/stage-kiss-tickets-279866
END:VEVENT
